{"tid":1750962,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"淺藍老母同深藍老豆去咗投票","createTime":"2019-11-24T14:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T15:50:12.000Z","uid":61161,"like":80,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"56319c730bd247728ec581fc42c4ae70fd1c6e68","tid":1750962,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"sorly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我無阻止佢哋投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而鼓勵老母去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後老母問我投邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我食晚飯果陣同佢哋作最後分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哂咗幾個月時間，應該將老母由淺藍轉咗做淺黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦都嘈到同老豆反咗面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後老母食完飯就去咗投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時間佢拉埋老豆去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆係偽中立深黑藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗兩邊各投一票都係打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知老豆一返到屋企就同我講話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持咗你喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成功加多2票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企4票，3黃票，1老人家棄票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算政見唔同，什麼求安穩，最後都敵不過兒子溫情牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd278989b2e2f2aeea39aa6587aeb4534c0bc2b3","tid":1750962,"uid":48889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"well done bro"},{"pid":"0e32e501fc7fef3aaac3f9182001e6d615b469a2","tid":1750962,"uid":126099,"like":14,"dislike":0,